pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; shoes plus socks.

Safety_Information.general_Info: When used as directed, this product does not present a hazard to humans or domestic animals. Causes moderate eye irritation.
Safety_Information.if_In_Eyes: Hold eye open and rinse slowly and gently with water for 15-20 minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present, after the first 5 minutes, then continue rinsing eye.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
